{"article_id":"xzoUZhRuHdrhykpA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former Vice President Joe Biden finally got the win","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he needed .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"After nearly a month of underperforming in Iowa and New Hampshire ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"and finishing in a distant second in Nevada ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Biden sealed a definitive win in the South Carolina primary ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"with black voters pushing him to victory .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"It 's the first primary win ever for Biden ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who is running for president for the third time .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"According to exit polls ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"64 % of black voters supported Biden .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders came in a distant second with black voters at 15 % ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"followed closely by billionaire activist Tom Steyer at 13 % .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Here are some takeaways from the South Carolina Democratic primary :","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"South Carolina voters also turned to a key endorsement","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to make their decision .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"According to exit polls ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"six out of 10 primary voters took into account Rep. Jim Clyburn 's endorsement of Biden .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Clyburn is a Democratic icon in South Carolina ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and told CNN on Friday","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"\" we will have to sit down","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"and get serious about how we retool this campaign \"","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"following Saturday 's primary .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Biden 's win gives him a much-needed boost","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"going into Super Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"where about 33 % of national pledged delegates are up for grabs .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"He has now leapfrogged into second place among national delegates ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"following Sanders .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"One hurdle","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"Biden will face ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"however ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"is competing with former New York City Mayor Mike Bloomberg for the first time this primary season .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"The two candidates are competing for much of the same center-left base ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"as is former mayor Pete Buttigieg and Sen. Amy Klobuchar .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"But Biden 's win will likely encourage voters and donors to move forward with supporting his campaign","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"- many of whom have been wary of the candidate","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"following his low standing in other early states .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Sanders is holding his lead in national delegates ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"but it 's clear the race is changing .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Saturday 's nights distant second place shows","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Sanders might see some trouble with some black voters ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"who make up one of the largest voting blocs in the Democratic Party .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Only 15 % of black voters supported Sanders in the South Carolina primary ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"according to exit polls .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"But nationally , Sanders has seen an increase in support among black voters .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"He stands at 29 % with black voters nationally ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"following Biden ,","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"who is leading at 31 % ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"according to an NBC News/Wall Street Journal poll .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"In 2016 , Sanders only won about 26 % total in South Carolina ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"compared to his then-Democratic opponent Hillary Clinton at about 73 % .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Joe Biden posts a convincing","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"- and quick -","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"win in South Carolina primary","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Sanders supporters denounce news outlets","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"calling SC primary for Biden 'with 0 % ' of the vote","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"In addition , Sanders is opting out of attending the Bridge Crossing Jubilee in Selma , Alabama ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"which commemorates Bloody Sunday on March 7 , 1965 ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that lead to the passage of the 1965 Voting Rights Act .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Alabama 's primary is part of Super Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Although Sanders is holding a lead in polling , both nationally and in several Super Tuesday states ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"it 's unclear whether Biden 's win Saturday will push some voters to turn to the former vice president .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Sanders , a Democratic socialist , appeals mostly with younger voters ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"who have traditionally not voted on the levels of older voters .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"However , in 2018 , 18-29 year-olds made up the largest increase in voter turnout .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"One state","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that could keep Sanders on top","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"is California .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"The Vermont Senator holds a huge lead in polling in the state ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"which has 415 delegates .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Candidates need to get at least 15 % across the state","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"to win delegates","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"and Sanders is the only one","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"who passed that threshold in a recent CNN poll ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"where he stood at 35 % .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Tom Steyer ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"who invested millions into the South Carolina primary ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"including about $ 18 million in TV ads alone ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"could n't break past Biden 's firewall .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Steyer ended his campaign","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"after finishing in a distant third place Saturday .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"`` I said","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"if I did n't see a path","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"to winning","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"that I 'd suspend my campaign ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"and honestly I ca n't see a path","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"where I can win the presidency , ''","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"he told supporters during a rally in Columbia , S , C .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Prior to dropping out ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Steyer had seen an increase in polling among black voters .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"He also received several high profile endorsements in the state ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"including Johnnie Cordero , chair of South Carolina 's Black Caucus .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Steyer did n't earn any delegates in Iowa , New Hampshire or Nevada","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"before dropping out .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"According to exit polls from The Washington Post ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Biden won with a whopping 60 % share of the votes","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"cast by African Americans in South Carolina ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"who accounted for more than half of the ballots in the Palmetto State .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"That level of support is even higher","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"than expected","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"after recent polls showed him with about 40 % support among black voters .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Biden ' s large share of the African American vote could foreshadow good things","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"if it carries over into Super Tuesday states with large populations of African American voters , such as North Carolina and Alabama .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"That voting bloc ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"who made up about a quarter of the votes","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"cast in the 2016 Democratic primary ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"could prove key","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"to making Biden competitive against Sanders on Super Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Black voters in Saturday ' s primary represented a lower percentage","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"( 56 % )","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"than those","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"who turned out in 2016 ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"when they made up 61 % of the South Carolina vote .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"But total turnout that year was 370,904 ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"compared with 528,720","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"( and counting )","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"votes in 2020 ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"meaning about 60,000 more black voters cast ballots in this contest than four years ago .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"If that level of turnout continues ,","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"that could be good news for the Biden campaign moving forward .","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"Donald Trump says","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"Mike Bloomberg should end 'joke of a campaign ' after South Carolina primary","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"It was n't a good night for former mayor Pete Buttigieg , Sen. Amy Klobuchar or Sen. Elizabeth Warren .","depth":4},{"id":126,"text":"Buttigieg ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"who saw strong finishes in Iowa and New Hampshire ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"fell flat in South Carolina .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"This comes","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"a week after placing a distant third in Nevada .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"In the weeks","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"leading up to South Carolina 's primary ,","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"Buttigieg continued to struggle with black voters ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"staying in the single digits among that bloc .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"This could spell trouble for Buttigieg going forward ,","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"where many of the states in Super Tuesday have a large population of black and Latino voters .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"Warren has continued to plateau","depth":5},{"id":138,"text":"as the primary continues .","depth":5},{"id":139,"text":"The Massachusetts Senator underperformed in New Hampshire","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"after placing third in Iowa .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"She also did n't do well in Nevada .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Despite having electric debate performances in the past two weeks ,","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"Warren has yet to find momentum at the polls .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"Klobuchar has n't been able to keep her momentum after a surprising third place New Hampshire win earlier this month .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"The Minnesota Senator has also struggled with voters of color ,","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"staying in the single digits with black and Latino voters .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"It 's unclear whether she will be able to break through the pack of the still crowded field of eight candidates .","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"But her home state of Minnesota is among those","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"that vote Tuesday .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":299,"left":0,"right":298,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":298,"left":273,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":244,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":171,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":161,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":151,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left"